@startuml
title Real Estate Token Issuance
actor "Real Estate Fund" as Fund
actor "Investor" as Investor
participant "Compliance System" as System
participant "Blockchain" as Chain

Fund -> System : Tokenize commercial property
System -> Investor : Verify qualification (KYC/AML via IdentityRegistry)
System -> System : Apply compliance rules (investment limits)
System -> Chain : Record transaction for auditing
Chain --> System : Confirmation of record
System --> Fund : Issuance completed
@enduml

@startuml
title Fund Subscription and Redemption
actor "Investor" as Investor
participant "Dashboard" as Dashboard
participant "Compliance System" as System
participant "Blockchain" as Chain

Investor -> Dashboard : Register and subscribe to tokens
Dashboard -> System : Validate compliance in real-time
System -> System : Verify configurable rules
System -> Chain : Record subscription
Chain --> System : Confirmation
Investor -> Dashboard : Request redemption
Dashboard -> System : Validate rules (lock-up)
System -> Chain : Record redemption
Chain --> System : Fund release
@enduml

@startuml
title Administrative Management
actor "Administrator" as Admin
participant "Admin Panel" as Panel
participant "Compliance System" as System
participant "Blockchain" as Chain

Admin -> Panel : Configure compliance rules
Panel -> System : Update rules
Admin -> Panel : Monitor transactions
Panel -> System : Generate reports
System -> System : Detect violation (e.g., volatility)
System -> Chain : Automatically pause transactions
Chain --> System : Pause confirmation
@enduml
